Protobuf wire format encoder/decoder Implements the basic protobuf binary format with varint encoding

Types

WireType = enum
  wtVarint = 0, wt64Bit = 1, wtLengthDelimited = 2, wtStartGroup = 3,
  wtEndGroup = 4, wt32Bit = 5
